snippet.title: Celebrate 10 YEARS of ONE DIRECTION with UNSEEN MOMENTS from Their Tours Over the Years!
snippet.description:
On July 23, 2010 - Harry Styles, Niall Horan, Louis Tomlinson, Liam Payne and Zayn Malik were put together as a group to form the global success known as One Direction! To celebrate the 10 year anniversary of this monumental day watch as we take you through some memorable moments with the boys on stage. We’ve collected some fan favourite moments and unseen clips of the boys from across their tours! 

#10YEARSOF1D #10YearsOfOneDirection

Listen to 1D: One Decade on iHeartRadio: https://www.iheart.com/live/1d-one-decade-8498/

snippet.title: Summer Morning Routine! *POPULAR GIRL vs NERDY BOY*
snippet.description:
Summer morning routine Girl vs Boy. Summer break is the best time of year. I love taking my time during bright summer mornings. This video shows the difference between two very different people. The girl is super girly and loves to have a long morning workout. She loves to pamper herself with a long shower. She has her shaving routine, hair care routine and of course her summer make up routine for a fun day at the beach. However, the boy, Raja, wakes up bright and early and loves to catch up on some reading and summer homework. He makes his way to his job and of course visits his crush at work. Both the boy and girl are sooo different. Get ready with me summer edition. Enjoy Popular Girl vs Nerdy Boy.

snippet.title: BAD BUNNY – Artist Spotlight Stories
snippet.description:
Produced by YouTube Music and directed by Kristian Mercado, Bad Bunny’s Artist Spotlight Story is a psychedelic portrait of a global superstar unlike any other. The film explores Bad Bunny’s origins in Puerto Rico, manifesting his dreams into reality, and how he uses his platform to speak out against social issues, all brought to life through vibrant animations and cutting-edge visuals to reflect his visionary aesthetic.

This spotlight story was filmed before the pandemic.

snippet.title: Midwest Cheap
snippet.description:
One man's trash is another man's... poncho 🗑️

Feat. Alex Wehrley and Josh Burstein

Follow me at these places: 
Twitter: @CharlieBerens
Instagram: @CharlieBerens
Facebook: www.facebook.com/charlieberensTV

For more Manitowoc Minute click here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRY-eAwoPfKBdGfuDu081r-bSMapeg0GB 
Manitowoc Minute T-shirts: www.manitowocminute.com

Manitowoc Minute host Charlie Berens goes to extreme lengths to stay frugal and cheap.  Charlie pours Carlo Rossi wine through a funnel, tries to cancel his Field and Stream subscription, and can't stand to see anything thrown away.  Charlie's wife Alex deals with his cheapness first hand which has been apparent from their first date to their anniversary.
